# Speech Recognition Module

## Установка зависимостей

### User

```sh
# cpu only version
pip install speechreclib[cpu]

# gpu version
pip install speechreclib[gpu]
```

### Dev

```sh
poetry env use 3.10 && poetry install
```

## Тестирование

### Юнит-тесты

```sh
tox
```

